  "instructions": [
    "Heat the sesame oil in the pressure cooker over medium heat.",
    "Add the grated ginger and minced garlic and cook until fragrant.",
    "Add the ground pork, if using, and cook until browned, breaking it up into small pieces.",
    "Add the soy sauce, rice vinegar, szechuan peppercorns, and red pepper flakes, and stir to combine.",
    "Add the cubed tofu and stir gently to combine.",
    "Add the chopped scallions and stir to combine.",
    "Close the lid of the pressure cooker and cook for 10 minutes.",
    "Let the pressure release naturally, then open the lid and stir the mapo tofu.",
    "Serve the mapo tofu over cooked jasmine rice."
